    "body": "and instead of the API @hokein suggested, how about\n\n``` js\ntype Progress = shape(\n  TotalBytes => float,\n  RecievedBytes => float\n)\nclass Downloads{\n  static setSavePath(path: String): void\n  static download(path: String[, savePath: String]): Download\n}\nclass Download extends EventEmitter{\n  savePath: String\n  onComplete(Callback: function(): void): void\n  onProgress(Callback: function(Progress): void): void\n  onAbort(Callback: function(hadError: bool): void): void\n  pause(): void\n  cancel()\n}\n```\n"
